dcterms:description: The Ising model dataset consists of spin configurations sampled from Boltzmann distributions at various temperatures, used to study phase transitions in a two-dimensional square-lattice ferromagnetic Ising model.

dcterms:description: The Stable Diffusion dataset is an image dataset generated by sampling images with prompts related to technology for each year, used to identify rapid changes in data distribution.
